Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 6.2°C) and outside temperature (up 5.6°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 6%).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 700 m), light levels (up 3828 lux), dew point temperature (down 1.6°C), and inside temperature (up 1.9°C) when compared to today.
